data.description: Here it is! This home is ready for you! There are 3 bedrooms, 2 & 1/2 bathrooms and 2 living areas! Enjoy your formal dining at night and your breakfast nook in the morning! The large flat yard has a storage area/workshop and there is a gate leading you into the back of your property toward the creek! You will be delighted with your full house filtration system, your newly paved additional parking area and your electricity savings from the Solar Panels!!! Sellers will pay off solar panels at closing!
